data.description: Beautiful Chicago Style Brick Bungalow, this home has been Meticulously kept, plenty of Living Space for a single person or a family. This home features an open-floor plan that flows from one room to the next. Full Bathroom on each level of this beauty, an amazing huge Master Suite upstairs, full basement for all your entertaining needs, plenty of storage. This home sits on an over-sized lot, huge deck for all your outdoor festivities. This home is nestled in a family-oriented neighborhood filled with long-term residents and ready for a new owner. Call Today for your personal showing...
